Subject: [PATCH 5/5] apalis-imx8x: use TEZI distro boot script

The distro boot script in TEZI image names boot-tezi.scr.
Enable using this particular name of script for u-boot images
which are used as a part of TEZI.

Related-to: TEI-791
Signed-off-by: Oleksandr Suvorov <oleksandr.suvorov@toradex.com>
---

 configs/apalis-imx8x_defconfig | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/configs/apalis-imx8x_defconfig b/configs/apalis-imx8x_defconfig
index d515e7b3a0..2005ca1d48 100644
--- a/configs/apalis-imx8x_defconfig
+++ b/configs/apalis-imx8x_defconfig
@@ -5,6 +5,7 @@ CONFIG_SYS_MALLOC_F_LEN=0x8000
 CONFIG_ENV_SIZE=0x2000
 CONFIG_ENV_OFFSET=0xFFFFDE00
 CONFIG_DM_GPIO=y
+CONFIG_TDX_EASY_INSTALLER=y
 CONFIG_BOOTAUX_RESERVED_MEM_BASE=0x88000000
 CONFIG_BOOTAUX_RESERVED_MEM_SIZE=0x08000000
 CONFIG_TARGET_APALIS_IMX8X=y
